    java.lang.Iterable<T>, BoundedFlowSet<T>, FlowSet<T>

    public class ArrayPackedSet<T>
extends AbstractBoundedFlowSet<T>
    Reference implementation for a BoundedFlowSet. Items are stored in an Array.
